You May Be Familiar With The Slogan, Let Us Spread Love And Not War. Well This Phrase Took Up A New Meaning For Residents Of Basil In Kajiado County On Saturday As Police Officers Joined A Local Church To Profess The Good News. The Officers, Who Are Part Of The General Service Unit (GSU), Highlighted Their Desire For Boosting Police And Community Relations. They Also Condemned The Circumstances In Which Fellow Police Officers Were Captured On Camera Using Excessive Office On A Student At The Jomo Kenyatta University Of Agriculture And Technology During A Riot Several Days Ago.